snippet.title: Rise of Agon - Teaser
snippet.description:
This is an official teaser for Rise of Agon, a hardcore sandbox MMORPG.
To sign up for our limited alpha waiting list please visit here:
http://www.riseofagon.com

Join the discussion:
http://forum.darkfallriseofagon.com/

Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/riseofagon/
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/riseofagon/
